headline: Ansys Announces Agreement to Offer Access to NVIDIA Omniverse Technology from within Simulation Solutions
summary: Ansys, part of Synopsys (NASDAQ: SNPS) and NVIDIA signed an agreement to license, sell, and support Omniverse technology embedded in Ansys simulation solutions. Through its integration of NVIDIA Omniverse™, Ansys will deliver easy access to Omniverse technologies and libraries to customers, starting with its CFD and autonomous solutions.
